<li id="cite_note-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFGuellecVan_Pottelsberghe_de_la_Potterie2004" class="citation journal cs1">Guellec, Dominique; Van Pottelsberghe de la Potterie, Bruno (July 2004). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1468-0084.2004.00083.x">"From R&amp;D to Productivity Growth: Do the Institutional Settings and the Source of Funds of R&amp;D Matter?"</a>. <i>Oxford Bulletin of Economics and Statistics</i>. <b>66</b> (3): 353–378. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1468-0084.2004.00083.x">10.1111/j.1468-0084.2004.00083.x</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/0305-9049">0305-9049</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:59568599">59568599</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Oxford+Bulletin+of+Economics+and+Statistics&amp;rft.atitle=From+R%26D+to+Productivity+Growth%3A+Do+the+Institutional+Settings+and+the+Source+of+Funds+of+R%26D+Matter%3F&amp;rft.volume=66&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=353-378&amp;rft.date=2004-07&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A59568599%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft.issn=0305-9049&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1111%2Fj.1468-0084.2004.00083.x&amp;rft.aulast=Guellec&amp;rft.aufirst=Dominique&amp;rft.au=Van+Pottelsberghe+de+la+Potterie%2C+Bruno&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.